						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in the <hi rend="italic">prākāra</hi> of the Mahāliṅgeśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 7th century.</p>						

						<p>The record, in characters of about the 7th century registers the death of Raṇamaṇḍe-Aṅgupesāra-Polegan, a servant of <hi rend="bold">Juddhamalla,</hi> in a fight with <hi rend="bold">Raṇakēsari</hi> who was entering Udayāpura, in the battle agains <hi rend="bold">Dharegīsa</hi> (the king ?). </p>						

						</summary>
